Package com.zfabrik.resources.util

Class ExpirableValuesPseudoMap<K,​V,​U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zfabrik.resources.util.ExpirableValuesPseudoMap<K,​V,​U>
  • public class ExpirableValuesPseudoMap<K,​V,​U>
extends java.lang.Object
    A map wrapper that manages a map over expirable values. Note: if an invalidation queue has been set, this map will NOT remove invalidated values from the map but relies on external processing to do so.
    Author:
    hb
